OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBlind man says Easyjet     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstaff 'refused to help' him
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A blind man has said Easyjet staff at  
OL,6, an airport would not sell him a ticket 
OL,7, in person and told him to use an app   
OL,8, instead.                               
OL,10,FMartin Conway and his wife, who are    
OL,11,Fboth blind, wanted to buy flights from 
OL,12,FLiverpool to Belfast after missing an  
OL,13,Fearlier plane due to traffic.          
OL,15,FHe said he was told he must book online
OL,16,Fbut no-one was able to assist him.     
OL,18,FEasyjet said it was "sorry to hear"    
OL,19,Fthat the couple did not receive the    
OL,20,Fservice they expected.                 
